# Trained YOLO Model

This folder contains the trained model used for ambulance detection.

## Model File

best.pt

This file is the trained YOLO model that detects ambulances in traffic camera footage.

## Model Information

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|------|
Model | YOLOv5 |
Framework | PyTorch |
Input Size | 640x640 |
Classes | Ambulance |

## Download Model

If the model file is not present, download it from:

Google Drive

or

HuggingFace

or

GitHub Release

Example:

https://drive.google.com/your-model-link

## Place Model Here

After downloading:

models
│
└── best.pt

## Training the Model

Example YOLOv5 training command:

python train.py --img 640 --batch 16 --epochs 100 --data data.yaml --weights yolov5s.pt

## Using the Model

Run the detection script:

python ai_detection/detect.py

The script will automatically load the model:

model = torch.hub.load(
    "ultralytics/yolov5",
    "custom",
    path="models/best.pt"
)